   <title>
    食環署封閉油麻地廟街兩食肆 截水截電封鎖所有出入口
   </title>
   <link>
    https://www.inmediahk.net/node/%E6%94%BF%E7%B6%93/%E9%A3%9F%E7%92%B0%E7%BD%B2%E5%B0%81%E9%96%89%E6%B2%B9%E9%BA%BB%E5%9C%B0%E5%BB%9F%E8%A1%97%E5%85%A9%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%86-%E6%88%AA%E6%B0%B4%E6%88%AA%E9%9B%BB%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%A3
   </link>
   <description>
    <![CDATA[<div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-18 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">內容: </div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/5030">政經</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fcolumn_images%2F202405091.jpg" width="940" height="492" alt="" /></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-19 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">自由標籤: </div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/528473">獨媒報導</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/501457">食環署</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/505148">廟街</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/507599">餐廳</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/539299">廟街小廚</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/539300">聯發小廚</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/533200">食肆</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p><font color="#e4692b">【獨媒報導】</font>食環署在今年4月30日獲庭頒布封閉令，封閉位於廟街兩間持續無牌經營及嚴重阻街的食物業處所。封閉令昨日（5月8日）生效，食環署指相關人員早上進入相關處所，移除可能引起火警危險的六個煤氣瓶和銷毀易腐壞的食物，兼截斷相關處所的食水及燃氣供應，並把所有出入口上鎖和加封。</p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/34ta0951T9" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53707786942_93edf25805_b.jpg" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
<p>兩間食肆分別為位於廟街29至35號地下C-D鋪的「廟街小廚」及A鋪的「聯發小廚」，食環署指兩間食肆均屬無牌經營，並長期霸佔行人通道和馬路，造成嚴重阻塞及環境衞生問題。在2022年7月至今年3月期間，食環署接獲437宗相關投訴，期間進行132次突擊執法行動，共提出306宗檢控。</p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/WZvRb0U17k" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53708910248_a5cdc9ef4b_b.jpg" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/69X917b1w6" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53709132140_d47b23736b_b.jpg" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
<p>食環署在4月30日獲法庭頒布封閉令，封閉兩間食肆。封閉令昨日生效，食環署指封閉令不設期限，相關處所的業主如採取措施確保違規情況不再出現，可向法庭申請解除封閉。食環署指根據《公眾衞生及市政條例》，除非獲署方書面許可，任何人不得進入或停留在已封處所中，違者最高可判罰款10萬元及監禁12個月，另每日罰款1,750元。任何人如移去或污損張貼於任何處所的封閉令，或破開或干擾在已封處所加上的鎖或封條，一經定罪最高可被判罰款2.5萬及監禁6個月。</p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/61e816c98a" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53709130850_8b064492bf_b.jpg" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/6WJB8FZv30" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53709028084_3efe5b0035_b.jpg" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
</div></div></div>]]>
